Privacy Policy
This privacy policy governs your use of the software application iman and iman Pro (“Application”) for mobile devices that was created by Adiman Muhammad.
The Application is a utility app to remind Muslim users of their Solah times based on their location
What information does the Application obtain and how is it used?
We do not collect any user’s personal information.
Does the Application collect precise real-time location information of the device?
When you use the mobile application, we may use GPS technology (or other similar technology) to get your current location in order to determine the city you are located. We will not share or collect or store your current location with other users or partners.
If you do not want us to use your location for the purposes set forth above, you should turn off the location services for the mobile application located in your mobile phone settings and/or within the mobile application.
Do third parties see and/or have access to information obtained by the Application?
We only collect usage information that is NOT linked to the device/user for analytics purposes
Changes
This Privacy Policy may be updated from time to time for any reason. You are advised to consult this Privacy Policy regularly for any changes, as continued use is deemed approval of all changes.
Contact us
If you have any questions regarding privacy while using the Application, or have questions about our practices, please contact us via email iman@adiman.net